8e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">AutoGEO为什么有效？</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">关键在于「规则」</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AutoGEO之所以能做到合作式优化，核心在于它找到了生成式引擎真正偏好的内容特征。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.21574074074074073\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1124\" data-height=\"243\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"121\" data-imgfileid=\"505202173\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e86c6d0c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FRvq8Ow69CYXL3FXGq3acEHv304fVUGVKfjWp4vv4YuvD4GGnjdrmkaFqjicHbNOdibKrNWic5SicGrDsSrFmejItUYz8cQb2w9vF3wzznkTWdx8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">AutoGEO框架概览</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">具体做法是：AutoGEO从大量真实的引擎行为数据中，让大模型自动提取偏好规则。流程分四步：对比高可见度和低可见度文档的差异（解释）、提炼核心因素（提取）、跨查询汇总（合并）、去噪留精（过滤）。最终得到一套可解释的规则集。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这套规则有两种使用方式：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AutoGEO API</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：直接把规则作为提示词注入GPT、Gemini等大模型API，即插即用。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AutoGEO Mini</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：用规则作为奖励信号，通过强化学习训练Qwen-3-1.7B小模型。部署成本极低，推理成本仅为API版的0.71%，可在CPU上离线运行。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">规则揭示了什么？对内容创作者的启示</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这部分发现对任何关注AI搜索的内容创作者都有参考价值。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.22592592592592592\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1368\" data-height=\"309\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"127\" data-imgfileid=\"505202177\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=204426a3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FRvq8Ow69CYVzkaOEzhzP9oJ0B8OVLx7IbDXPqcJL3ib2qN7LWr91Vc1RlRTQt8HsR5lTHg4LiaQXA2Wp6CGlps6DqO8J5pib0YVhnwbTib6tpwA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">不同引擎和数据集间的规则重叠与迁移性能</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">发现一：不同AI引擎的偏好大同小异。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;相同数据集上，Gemini、GPT、Claude三个引擎的偏好规则重叠率在79%到84%之间。这意味着「好内容」的标准在不同AI引擎之间是相通的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">发现二：不同领域的偏好差异很大。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;通用研究类问题的规则重叠高达88%，但电商领域降到35%。研究领域偏好「深度解释」和「因果分析」，电商领域偏好「可操作的步骤指引」和「模块化信息结构」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">发现三：定制规则始终最优，但通用规则也有效。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;为特定引擎和领域量身提取的规则效果最好，但即使直接迁移其他引擎的规则，也能显著优于不使用规则的基线。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这些发现给内容创作者一个清晰的信号：与其靠「投毒」这种短期行为博曝光，不如理解AI引擎真正偏好什么，按规则优化内容。后者不仅效果更好，还不会伤害搜索生态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">AI搜索的信任问题</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">需要「合作」来解</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">回到开头的问题：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">卖广告、投毒，AI搜索还能不「瞎说」吗？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果整个行业都走前两条路（卖广告+对抗式投毒），AI搜索的可信度确实会持续下降。但AutoGEO指出了一种不同的可能性：合作式GEO可以在「显著」提升内容可见度的同时，搜索质量纹丝不动。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这不只是一个学术结论，更是AI搜索生态可持续发展的方向。当3000元就能污染AI搜索的回答时，行业需要的不是更高的围墙，而是更好的规则。正确的GEO不是给AI投毒，而是让优质内容被AI更好地「看见」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/cxcscmu/AutoGEO\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/cxcscmu/AutoGEO</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文介绍了 CMU 提出的 AutoGEO 框架，这是一种合作式生成引擎优化（GEO）方法，旨在提升内容可见度的同时维护搜索质量，对抗「投毒式」对抗 GEO 乱象。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文介绍了 CMU 提出的 AutoGEO 框架，这是一种合作式生成引擎优化（GEO）方法，旨在提升内容可见度的同时维护搜索质量，对抗「投毒式」对抗 GEO 乱象。",
  "summary": "针对 AI 搜索商业化过程中出现的平台广告和第三方「投毒式」GEO（生成引擎优化）乱象，本文深入解读了来自 CMU 的 ICLR 2026 论文《AutoGEO》。该研究提出了一种「合作式 GEO」新思路，通过自动提取 AI 引擎的偏好规则，指导内容创作者进行正向优化。实验数据表明，AutoGEO 在提升内容可见度（最高达 50.99%）的同时，能保持甚至提升主流引擎（Gemini、GPT、Claude）的搜索质量（GEU），有效解决了传统对抗式方法导致的搜索效用下降问题。文章还揭示了不同领域和引擎间的偏好差异，为 AI 时代的内容生态建设提供了可持续发展的技术方案。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 搜索面临「平台广告」与「对抗式 GEO 投毒」的双重信任危机。",
      "explanation": "平台广告侵蚀用户信任，而第三方服务商通过批量发布虚假内容「投毒」AI 模型，虽提升了可见度却严重破坏了搜索质量。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AutoGEO 倡导「合作式 GEO」，实现内容方、平台与用户的正和博弈。",
      "explanation": "不同于损人利己的对抗式方法，合作式 GEO 通过理解引擎偏好来优化优质内容，在不损害搜索效用的前提下提升曝光。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AutoGEO 通过自动提取可解释的偏好规则来指导内容优化。",
      "explanation": "该框架包含规则提取、合并与过滤流程，并提供高性能的 API 版本及极低成本的强化学习小模型版本（AutoGEO Mini）。"
    },
    {
      "point": "主流 AI 引擎对「好内容」的偏好具有高度一致性，但领域差异显著。",
      "explanation": "不同引擎间的规则重叠率超 80%，但研究领域偏好深度解释，而电商领域更看重模块化信息和操作指引。"
    }
  ],
